ms.safi.btsync.dto

Class Secrets

  • Object
    • ms.safi.btsync.dto.Secrets

  • public class Secrets
extends Object
    JavaBean implementation of a set of secrets. These secrets are the read_only, read_write, and encryption (if available) to use for sharing a folder.

    An example of a set of secrets: 

     {
      "read_only": "ECK2S6MDDD7EOKKJZOQNOWDTJBEEUKGME",
      "read_write": "DPFABC4IZX33WBDRXRPPCVYA353WSC3Q6",
      "encryption": "G3PNU7KTYM63VNQZFPP3Q3GAMTPRWDEZ”
 }
    Author:
    Omeed Safi
